{"tid":1172294,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗亂屙落梳化,諗唔明","createTime":"2019-05-26T10:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T17:15:48.000Z","uid":132900,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b95893cf65957b3519121f84e5b760d77aabca19","tid":1172294,"uid":132900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:33:50.000Z","msg":"我都養左佢七八年，係舊屋一直有個位比佢屙尿既。<br />\n咁當然有一兩次係梳化屙過，唔知係咪咁張梳化就算洗過都有佢啲味。<br />\n到搬左屋諗住早晚帶佢落街屙清就唔洗係屋企屙啦，一開始兩三個月都好乖既。點知有一次又係梳化屙，幾滴都屙，之後每日就算我地帶佢行街屙哂佢都係照係梳化屙幾滴，無野都揾野搞張梳化，每次佢屙完我地都有鬧佢同表現到嬲左佢咁無乜摸佢。<br />\n究竟佢係因為我地唔摸佢而屙定係因為屋企無佢廁所先屙落去梳化。<br />\n<br />\n利申：佢本身係勁細膽同勁嗲既狗狗黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇唔透"},{"pid":"a43ea7ca7e4bd70b05ac6350b4b7030c2900f53f","tid":1172294,"uid":58445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"屋企無廁所？咁你想佢屙邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb8f306dcd2bcd7c74d7fa6a7af9d914328575a","tid":1172294,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:36:02.000Z","msg":"你老母：屋企隻毒撚射精落紙巾, 諗唔明"},{"pid":"9c7815179d2e56fb91aa1b901e2e67f5099c2347","tid":1172294,"uid":42595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"我隻狗 接近同你一樣 7 8歲 亂痾左一年 鬧又試過 扮唔知又試過 襯你見唔到先破壞痾  幾滴都會咇出黎"},{"pid":"0a3dd7cab68c733b6786d678a00e117ca0b62a9b","tid":1172294,"uid":132900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a43ea7ca7e4bd70b05ac6350b4b7030c2900f53f","tid":1172294,"uid":58445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"屋企無廁所？咁你想佢屙邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"整過個比佢佢唔屙，係落街先屙。頭三個月都無事。<img src=\"/assets/fac